OL,6,FDr Dash interviewed more than 100
OL,7,Fstaff at the regulator, received some
OL,8,F125 emails and also spoke to around
OL,9,F200 senior managers, caregivers and
OL,10,Fclinicians in the NHS and social care,
OL,11,Fas well as patient groups.
