OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FShe concluded there were serious
OL,7,Ffailings in the internal workings of
OL,8,Fthe CQC "which have led to a
OL,9,Fsubstantial loss of credibility within
OL,10,Fthe health and social care sectors, a
OL,11,Fdeterioration in the ability of CQC to
OL,12,Fidentify poor performance and support
OL,13,Fa drive to improve quality ` and a
OL,14,Fdirect impact on the capacity and
OL,15,Fcapability of both the social care and
OL,16,Fthe healthcare sectors to deliver much-
OL,17,Fneeded improvements in care."
