OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FOn poor operational performance, Dr
OL,7,FDash pointed to the "stark reduction
OL,8,Fin activity" highlighted in her
OL,9,Finterim report, with just 6,700
OL,10,Finspections and assessments carried
OL,11,Fout in 2023, compared with almost
OL,12,F15,800 in 2019 before the pandemic.
OL,14,FThis has resulted in new health and
OL,15,Fcare organisations joining a "backlog"
OL,16,Fto be registered by the CQC, delays in
OL,17,Fre-inspecting hospitals and units
OL,18,Ffollowing a 'requires improvement' or
OL,19,F'inadequate' rating and some ratings
OL,20,Fbeing years old.
