OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,F"The review has concluded that poor
OL,7,Foperational performance is impacting
OL,8,FCQC's ability to ensure that health
OL,9,Fand social care services provide
OL,10,Fpeople with safe, effective and
OL,11,Fcompassionate care, negatively
OL,12,Fimpacting the opportunity to improve
OL,13,Fhealth and social care services and,
OL,14,Fin some cases, for providers to
OL,15,Fdeliver services at all," the report
OL,16,Fsaid.
