OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FThe study also found profound problems
OL,7,Fwith IT systems introduced from 2021
OL,8,Fby the CQC, with people saying they
OL,9,Fcaused more delay and were difficult
OL,10,Fto use.
OL,12,FWhen it came to inspections, Dr Dash
OL,13,Ffound delays to producing reports,
OL,14,Fwith some hospitals and care providers
OL,15,Fwaiting "several months" to receive
OL,16,Freports and ratings following
OL,17,Fassessments.
