OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FThe review team heard multiple
OL,7,Fcomments about poor-quality reports,
OL,8,Fincluding from patients, such as
OL,9,Fconfusing messages and unclear
OL,10,Ffindings.
OL,12,FDr Dash argued there has been a "loss
OL,13,Fof expertise" among staff, including
OL,14,Famong inspectors, and concerns around
OL,15,Fthe CQC's single assessment framework
OL,16,F(SAF), which was set up to give 34
OL,17,Fareas of care quality that could be
OL,18,Fapplied to any provider of health or
OL,19,Fsocial care.
