OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FHer review found the SAF uses "vague
OL,7,Flanguage" and there is "limited
OL,8,Finformation available for providers
OL,9,Fand users or patients as to what care
OL,10,Flooks like under each of the ratings
OL,11,Fcategories".
OL,13,FFurthermore, there is "insufficient
OL,14,Fattention paid to the effectiveness of
OL,15,Fcare and a lack of focus on outcomes"
OL,16,Ffor users and patients.
