OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FDr Dash found a "lack of clarity"
OL,7,Fregarding how the CQC calculates
OL,8,Fratings and "concerning use of the
OL,9,Foutcome of previous inspections (that
OL,10,Foften took place several years ago) to
OL,11,Fcalculate a current rating".
OL,13,FThe report said "providers do not
OL,14,Funderstand how ratings are calculated
OL,15,Fand, as a result, believe it is a
OL,16,Fcomplicated algorithm, or a 'magic
OL,17,Fbox'".
