OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FIn response to the review,
OL,7,Fcommissioned by the previous
OL,8,Fgovernment in May, Health and Social
OL,9,FCare Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,10,F"Patient safety is the bedrock of a
OL,11,Fhealthy NHS and social care system.
OL,13,F"That's why we are taking steps to
OL,14,Freform the CQC, to root out poor
OL,15,Fperformance and ensure patients can
OL,16,Fhave confidence in its ratings once
OL,17,Fagain.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@AOU
