OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,F"This Government will never turn a
OL,7,Fblind eye to failure. An overly
OL,8,Fcomplex system of healthcare
OL,9,Fregulation and oversight is no good
OL,10,Ffor patients or providers.
OL,12,F"We will overhaul the system to make
OL,13,Fit effective and efficient, to protect
OL,14,Fpatient safety."
OL,16,FMr Streeting has now requested that Dr
OL,17,FDash carries out two further reviews,
OL,18,Ffocusing on patient safety and quality.
