OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FThe first will explore the remits of
OL,7,Fsix organisations and examine if
OL,8,Fpatient safety can be bolstered
OL,9,Fthrough a different approach.
OL,11,FThe organisations include the CQC and
OL,12,Fthe maternity programme, Healthwatch
OL,13,FEngland, the Local Healthwatch
OL,14,Fnetwork, the National Guardian's
OL,15,FOffice, the Health Services Safety
OL,16,FInvestigation Body, the Patient Safety
OL,17,FCommissioner and NHS Resolution.
