OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FThe second review will look at quality
OL,7,Fand governance, with the findings
OL,8,Fshaping the Government's 10-year plan
OL,9,Fto transform the health service.
OL,11,FSaffron Cordery, deputy chief
OL,12,Fexecutive, NHS Providers, said:
OL,13,F"Keeping patients safe is the number
OL,14,Fone priority for NHS trust leaders.
OL,16,F"Trust leaders have said for some time
OL,17,Fthat the regulator needs urgent
OL,18,Freform. Restoring the CQC's
OL,19,Fcredibility will take a lot of work.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@AOU
