OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,F"Regulation of NHS services is
OL,7,Fimportant but to add value it needs
OL,8,Feffective leadership, the right
OL,9,Fexpertise and a focus on what really
OL,10,Fmatters. We have highlighted that the
OL,11,FCQC must concentrate more on support
OL,12,Fand improvement.
OL,14,F"With two new reviews announced which
OL,15,Fwill focus on patient safety and
OL,16,Fquality, trust leaders are ready and
OL,17,Fwilling to work with the CQC and all
OL,18,Fother key organisations as they strive
OL,19,Fto provide high-quality services for
OL,20,Fpatients and in their quest to keep
OL,21,Fimproving and innovating."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU}D@ZO]
