OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FThe CQC said in response that it would
OL,7,Fappoint at least three chief
OL,8,Finspectors to lead on regulation and
OL,9,Fimprovement of hospitals, primary care
OL,10,Fsuch as GP and dental services, and
OL,11,Fadult social care services.
OL,13,F"Consideration will also be given to
OL,14,Fwhether a fourth chief inspector is
OL,15,Fneeded to lead on regulation and
OL,16,Fimprovement of mental health
OL,17,Fservices," it said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@JO]
