OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FThe current method for assessing
OL,7,Fhospitals and other organisations will
OL,8,Falso be made simpler and enable the
OL,9,FCQC to carry out and report on
OL,10,Finspections more quickly, it said.
OL,12,FThe five current questions asked of
OL,13,FNHS and social care services (safe,
OL,14,Feffective, caring, responsive and well-
OL,15,Fled) will be kept, but 34 separate
OL,16,Fquality statements will be looked at
OL,17,Fto "ensure clarity and remove
OL,18,Fduplication".
OL,26,@yD@DOUzD@LO]
