OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FThe CQC also promised to improve the
OL,7,Fway it deals with the NHS and social
OL,8,Fcare sector, and will pause assessment
OL,9,Fof integrated care systems (ICS) for
OL,10,Fsix months.
OL,12,FThe CQC has previously asked Professor
OL,13,FSir Mike Richards to carry out an
OL,14,Finternal review, which will also be
OL,15,Fpublished on Tuesday.
OL,17,FIan Dilks, chairman of the CQC, said
OL,18,Fit accepted the Dash findings and "we
OL,19,Fwill address the recommendations with
OL,20,Furgency".
OL,26,@zD@cOU|D@HO]
