OL,3,CNHS and care regulator needs 'rapid
OL,4,Cturnaround', report finds
OL,6,FHe said both the Dash review and that
OL,7,Ffrom Sir Mike "have reaffirmed the
OL,8,Fsupport for a robust health and care
OL,9,Fregulator and recognised the
OL,10,Fdedication and experience of CQC
OL,11,Fstaff".
OL,13,F"We are committed to rebuilding trust
OL,14,Fin CQC's regulation and are taking
OL,15,Faction to make sure we have the right
OL,16,Fstructure, processes, and technology
OL,17,Fin place to help us fulfil our vital
OL,18,Frole of helping people get good care
OL,19,Fand supporting providers to improve,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
